quote><br />\n一直吹奏x係咩心態<br />\n唔講錢問題 <br />\n個樣又柒M字額<br />\n又印多問題<br />\n其實已經好多報導都講到跑分8+&gt;8&gt;x<br />\n除非係想玩新技術 （白老鼠）or 好似上面班小學雞一樣 用X黎show off <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母用部X講到自己好撚有米咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n申利返先 用過x 賣返換8+ 爽到仆街</blockquote><br />\n繼續吹啦傻仔 不過冇人知你用8嫁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用部電話姐 好用唔柒咪得 用部X都自視過高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19821ef87ff3cd502aec5826129c07b4cccddeec","tid":503280,"uid":2404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:09:38.000Z","msg":"8,一定係8"},{"pid":"400ee27369a89e8518b0433684dfecb8e5abb699","tid":503280,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:23:21.000Z","msg":"X啦，一、兩年後有烙印會賣得貴過8/plus<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"059c46b1dde8b0952c8362ddcb00e8ce4cd0e561","tid":503280,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\nX會變主流 8呢類機只會變成窮撚專用機</blockquote><br />\n你見連登仔成日話樓價貴，又吹奏公屋就知大部分都係窮撚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n買唔起X又要同人講自己換左新機果班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 可惜冇人知佢用新機 因為真係冇分別 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要比人知你窮定有錢已經on9<br />\n要用部電話話比人知你有錢換新機，更加on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8 貴 7 少少，但玩多年就係玩多年<br />\n如果想買x 就等多代啦，Apple 等2/4代先買得過</blockquote><br />\n羅輯已經 FAIL<br />\nX唔可以玩多幾年？faceid可以有排玩 我3gs由開始用<br />\n3&gt;gs4&gt;4s&gt;5&gt;6&gt;6s&gt;7&gt;x<br />\n用左咁多年 部X真係最正<br />\n你咪繼續停留係上世紀囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話好多APPS 唔支援 到底你有冇真正用過呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nAnyway 8就真係最後一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nX 有印，完</blockquote><br />\n講左咁耐都係講果張圖 就咁多人話有印 唔通你地都係共用同一部X？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n果個開左8-10 個鐘既demo機 畫面一直係果個先整到有印，講真有邊撚個會咁用機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要有印係隔一陣就無，咁都吹咁耐"},{"pid":"56402b8f148ee3cbbb1a3eaf1f42c8f7d51d70f1","tid":503280,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>x真係好撚樣衰</blockquote><br />\n一直吹奏x係咩心態<br />\n唔講錢問題 <br />\n個樣又柒M字額<br />\n又印多問題<br />\n其實已經好多報導都講到跑分8+&gt;8&gt;x<br />\n除非係想玩新技術 （白老鼠）or 好似上面班小學雞一樣 用X黎show off <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母用部X講到自己好撚有米咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n申利返先 用過x 賣返換8+ 爽到仆街</blockquote><br />\n淨係睇過cpu X屌打全球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808d9308bf612d9ce74dfba33a87c95536a65dc9","tid":503280,"uid":17920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>x真係好撚樣衰</blockquote><br />\n一直吹奏x係咩心態<br />\n唔講錢問題 <br />\n個樣又柒M字額<br />\n又印多問題<br />\n其實已經好多報導都講到跑分8+&gt;8&gt;x<br />\n除非係想玩新技術 （白老鼠）or 好似上面班小學雞一樣 用X黎show off <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你老母用部X講到自己好撚有米咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇啱邊部咪用邊部<br />\n吹奏x用電話黎區分有錢定窮撚<br />\n班友真係毒到一個點。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79723e85ee23fc79e81b8ebc53e3231969a244fa","tid":503280,"uid":52525,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"本身6仔 都想買8+ 256<br />\n但睇返舊錢同X差唔多<br />\n所以都猶豫左好耐<br />\n<br />\n不過本身又唔